name: Zubababanchou - Gagaga Coat
desc: If this card is in your hand and you control a "Zubaba" monster or "Gagaga" monster, except "Zubababanchou - Gagaga Coat": You can Special Summon this card. You can target 1 "Gogogo" monster or "Dododo" monster in your GY; Special Summon it, also you cannot Special Summon monsters from the Extra Deck for the rest of this turn, except Xyz Monsters. You can only use each effect of "Zubababanchou - Gagaga Coat" once per turn.
